    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock. The vehicle retains its structural rigidity and low center of gravity thanks to the factory carbon fiber roof. To address common platform concerns, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced. The hydraulic steering remains communicative, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offers a versatile range of compression and rebound settings. This is a mechanically sound specimen for the purist seeking the final chapter of the naturally aspirated M-engine legacy.",
